snippet.title: The Sims 4 Cool Kitchen Stuff: Official Trailer
snippet.description:
Give your kitchen a makeover with The Sims 4 Cool Kitchen Stuff!
 
Learn more about this Stuff Pack: http://o.ea.com/41141
 
Add sleek appliances and furnishings to redesign the kitchen with a modern flare and discover what surprising flavors your Sims can create with the all-new ice cream maker.
